    "description": "<p><span style=\"font-family: DDG_ProximaNova, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_0, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_1, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_2, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_3, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_4, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_5, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_6, 'Proxima Nova', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', sans-serif\">This wand generates a cone of fear that extends 60 feet long and 30 feet wide at its far end. Anyone caught within the cone must make a saving throw against wands or flee from the user at three times their normal speed for 30 rounds.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: DDG_ProximaNova, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_0, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_1, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_2, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_3, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_4, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_5, DDG_ProximaNova_UI_6, 'Proxima Nova', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', sans-serif\">This wand is crafted from dark, polished wood, featuring a sleek and slightly curved design. At the end, it is adorned with a menacing skull motif, intricately carved and detailed, giving it a foreboding presence. The skull's eye sockets glow faintly with an eerie light, while the shaft of the wand is etched with subtle, arcane symbols.</span></p>",
